  "detailed_description": "Car Constructor will allow you to build, repair and paint your own car, then check it out on the race track!  This game offers you a lot of tools for repairing and improving the car, a shop with a wide selection of spare parts, various types of paint and tuning, as well as a realistic mountain track and various types of road surface.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Main Features</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Deep upgrade system of the car. You can replace almost any part<br></li><li> Detailed ride physics<br></li><li> Realistic graphics, big race track<br></li><li> A real car enthusiast's garage!</li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "Car Constructor will allow you to build, repair and paint your own car, then check it out on the race track!  This game offers you a lot of tools for repairing and improving the car, a shop with a wide selection of spare parts, various types of paint and tuning, as well as a realistic mountain track and various types of road surface.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Main Features</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Deep upgrade system of the car. You can replace almost any part<br></li><li> Detailed ride physics<br></li><li> Realistic graphics, big race track<br></li><li> A real car enthusiast's garage!</li></ul>",
